{
  "total_duration": 795.039,
  "lines": [
    {
      "i": 0,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 5.576,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的题目是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Food and talk"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，中文是“进餐与交谈”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 5.926,
      "end": 15.606,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这课不是 food lesson，也不是评价谁吃饭好不好看。它是一场 dinner-table small talk comedy，餐桌寒暄喜剧。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 15.956,
      "end": 25.303,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "dinner party"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是普通晚饭，而是比较正式的 invited meal，有客人、有座位、有 hostess。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 25.653,
      "end": 34.325,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "hostess"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是女主人，the woman who invites and looks after guests。她可能会安排客人坐在哪里。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 34.675,
      "end": 45.523,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以主人公被安排坐在 Mrs. Rumbold 旁边。他不认识她，只好做一件很英语的事："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "make conversation"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，礼貌地找话题。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 45.873,
      "end": 54.601,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Make conversation"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是审问，也不是考试，而是递一个轻一点的话题，看对方愿不愿意接。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 54.951,
      "end": 63.271,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可是 Mrs. Rumbold 很 serious and reserved。她没有抬头，眼睛一直看着盘子，很快就开始吃饭。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 63.62,
      "end": 76.484,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "主人公连续递出三个 polite future questions："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Will you be seeing it?"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Will you be spending your holidays abroad?"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Will you be staying in England?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 76.834,
      "end": 80.53,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "每一次，她都只回答："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "No."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 80.88,
      "end": 90.16,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后他 desperate 了，问她饭吃得开不开心。她终于说了一整句：如果你多吃点、少说点，我们两个都会更享受这顿饭。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 90.51,
      "end": 107.27,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "整课记忆链是：dinner party -> hostess -> sit next to Mrs. Rumbold -> eyes fixed on plate -> busy eating -> make conversation -> The Globe -> holidays abroad -> staying in England -> in despair -> ate more and talked less。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 107.62,
      "end": 117.308,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一幅画，是 seat arranged。课文一开始说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Last week at a dinner party, the hostess asked me to sit next to Mrs. Rumbold."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 117.657,
      "end": 123.825,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "dinner party"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是 formal meal with guests，不是随便在家吃一顿。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 124.175,
      "end": 131.287,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "hostess"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是女主人，她安排座位，所以主人公被请去坐在 Mrs. Rumbold 旁边。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 131.637,
      "end": 139.877,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这个开头很重要：他不是主动去打扰陌生人，而是在正式聚餐里被安排坐到一个不熟的人旁边。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 140.227,
      "end": 151.627,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这种场景今天也会发生：school dinner, camp meal, parents' friends' gathering, or host-family dinner。你坐在不熟的人旁边，就会需要 polite small talk。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 151.977,
      "end": 161.193,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二幅画，是 eyes on the plate。课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Mrs. Rumbold was a large, unsmiling lady in a tight black dress."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 161.543,
      "end": 175.662,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "我们要尊重地理解这个描写。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "unsmiling"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是 not smiling，表情严肃；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "tight black dress"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是她穿着贴身黑裙，不是拿外貌开玩笑。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 176.012,
      "end": 181.38,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "接着课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "She did not even look up when I took my seat beside her."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 19,
      "start": 181.73,
      "end": 187.586,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "look up"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是抬头看；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "beside"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "就是 next to。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 20,
      "start": 187.936,
      "end": 195.799,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "她的注意力在哪里？课文很清楚："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Her eyes were fixed on her plate and in a short time, she was busy eating."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 21,
      "start": 196.149,
      "end": 205.789,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "fixed on"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "表示一直盯着；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "in a short time"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是 soon。不久，她就忙着吃起来了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 22,
      "start": 206.139,
      "end": 213.179,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这幅画的重点不是“她不好”，而是 she is not inviting conversation。她可能只想安静吃饭。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 23,
      "start": 213.529,
      "end": 221.265,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三幅画，是 polite questions, short answers。课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I tried to make conversation."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 24,
      "start": 221.615,
      "end": 228.542,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "主人公先找了一个安全话题：theatre。他说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "A new play is coming to \"The Globe\" soon."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 25,
      "start": 228.892,
      "end": 239.692,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "play"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里是 theatre performance，舞台剧，不是 play a game。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The Globe"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是剧场名字。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 26,
      "start": 240.042,
      "end": 254.53,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "小提醒："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "globe"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "小写时可以是 earth, world, or a round model of the earth；但"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The Globe"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "大写时，在这课里就是 proper name，剧场名。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 27,
      "start": 254.88,
      "end": 263.071,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "然后他问："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Will you be seeing it?"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里不是问眼睛会不会看见，而是 will you go to see the play?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 28,
      "start": 263.421,
      "end": 265.957,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "她回答："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "No."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 29,
      "start": 266.307,
      "end": 275.895,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他又换 travel 话题："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Will you be spending your holidays abroad this year?"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "abroad"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是 in another country，在国外。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 30,
      "start": 276.245,
      "end": 278.701,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "她还是："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "No."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 31,
      "start": 279.05,
      "end": 283.69,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他再换一个更近的话题："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Will you be staying in England?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 32,
      "start": 284.04,
      "end": 286.496,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "她还是："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "No."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 33,
      "start": 286.846,
      "end": 295.326,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "你能听见这个尴尬节奏：polite topic -> No；new polite topic -> No；one more topic -> No。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 34,
      "start": 295.676,
      "end": 304.108,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第四幅画，是 final line。课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "In despair, I asked her whether she was enjoying her dinner."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 35,
      "start": 304.458,
      "end": 312.634,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "despair"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在这里不是悲剧式绝望，而是 social despair：他已经没有话题可递了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 36,
      "start": 312.984,
      "end": 320.255,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "whether she was enjoying her dinner"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是 indirect question，意思是她饭吃得是否愉快。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 37,
      "start": 320.605,
      "end": 328.853,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "然后 Mrs. Rumbold 终于说了一整句："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Young man, if you ate more and talked less, we would both enjoy our dinner!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 38,
      "start": 329.203,
      "end": 336.363,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这句话先听意思，不要先上重语法：多吃点，少说点，我们两个都会开心。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 39,
      "start": 336.713,
      "end": 343.313,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "反转就在这里：he thought conversation would make dinner better；she thought silence would make dinner better。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 40,
      "start": 343.663,
      "end": 351.343,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以这课不是教你一直聊，而是教你：politeness includes speaking, and also noticing when to stop。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 41,
      "start": 351.693,
      "end": 354.213,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这一课最容易误会的地方是什么？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 42,
      "start": 354.563,
      "end": 357.768,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "以为 Mrs. Rumbold 是被拿来嘲笑的人？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 43,
      "start": 358.118,
      "end": 367.278,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对，所以我们要守住 tone。她是 serious, reserved, focused on eating，不是 caricature，不是外貌笑话。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 44,
      "start": 367.628,
      "end": 369.945,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那主人公做错了吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 45,
      "start": 370.295,
      "end": 379.543,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他一开始没有错。他在 dinner party 被安排坐在陌生人旁边，试着"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "make conversation"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，这是礼貌。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 46,
      "start": 379.893,
      "end": 382.855,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可是她一直回答"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "No"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 47,
      "start": 383.205,
      "end": 391.005,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对，这就是社交信号。Short answers often mean the topic is not working, or the person does not want to continue."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 48,
      "start": 391.355,
      "end": 397.654,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Will you be seeing it?"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "为什么不直接说"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Will you see it?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 49,
      "start": 398.004,
      "end": 409.028,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这就是今天的 language point。加上"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "be doing"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，问题听起来像在问“这会不会是你的安排之一”，而不是硬问“你到底做不做”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 50,
      "start": 409.378,
      "end": 415.06,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Will you be doing...?"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "比较像 gentle small-talk question？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 51,
      "start": 415.41,
      "end": 422.79,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "Exactly. It is useful when you want to ask about future plans softly, especially with someone you do not know well."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 52,
      "start": 423.14,
      "end": 427.196,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那最后她说 eat more and talk less，是不是很 rude？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 53,
      "start": 427.546,
      "end": 436.626,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "有一点 sharp，所以它才是 punchline。但我们也要看见她的边界：she did not want more talk at dinner."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 54,
      "start": 436.976,
      "end": 442.04,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Last week at a dinner party, the hostess asked me to sit next to Mrs. Rumbold."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 55,
      "start": 442.389,
      "end": 447.093,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Mrs. Rumbold was a large, unsmiling lady in a tight black dress."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 56,
      "start": 447.443,
      "end": 451.163,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "She did not even look up when I took my seat beside her."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 57,
      "start": 451.513,
      "end": 456.169,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Her eyes were fixed on her plate and in a short time, she was busy eating."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 58,
      "start": 456.519,
      "end": 459.087,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I tried to make conversation."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 59,
      "start": 459.437,
      "end": 462.941,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "'A new play is coming to \"The Globe\" soon,' I said."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 60,
      "start": 463.291,
      "end": 465.475,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "'Will you be seeing it?'"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 61,
      "start": 465.825,
      "end": 467.961,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "'No,' she answered."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 62,
      "start": 468.311,
      "end": 473.423,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "'Will you be spending your holidays abroad this year?' I asked."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 63,
      "start": 473.772,
      "end": 475.908,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "'No,' she answered."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 64,
      "start": 476.258,
      "end": 480.338,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "'Will you be staying in England?' I asked."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 65,
      "start": 480.688,
      "end": 482.824,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "'No,' she answered."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 66,
      "start": 483.174,
      "end": 487.254,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "In despair, I asked her whether she was enjoying her dinner."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 67,
      "start": 487.604,
      "end": 492.884,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "'Young man,' she answered, 'if you ate more and talked less, we would both enjoy our dinner!'"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 68,
      "start": 493.234,
      "end": 495.946,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "hostess"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一个词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "hostess"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 69,
      "start": 496.296,
      "end": 497.952,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "hostess"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "hostess"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 70,
      "start": 498.302,
      "end": 505.533,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "hostess"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "hostess"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是 the woman who invites and looks after guests at a meal or event，女主人。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 71,
      "start": 505.883,
      "end": 510.495,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "hostess"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the hostess asked me to sit next to Mrs. Rumbold"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 72,
      "start": 510.845,
      "end": 519.285,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "hostess"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这说明主人公的座位不是随便坐的，是 hostess 安排的。正式聚餐里，座位安排会把故事推到陌生人寒暄。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 73,
      "start": 519.635,
      "end": 525.899,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "hostess"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "也顺手记住"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "sit next to"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，就是 sit beside，坐在旁边。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 74,
      "start": 526.249,
      "end": 529.777,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "make"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二个词组："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "make conversation"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 75,
      "start": 530.126,
      "end": 532.262,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "make"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "make conversation"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 76,
      "start": 532.612,
      "end": 540.9,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "make"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Make conversation"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是 make light, polite talk，找一点轻松礼貌的话题，尤其是和不太熟的人。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 77,
      "start": 541.25,
      "end": 544.686,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "make"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I tried to make conversation."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 78,
      "start": 545.036,
      "end": 557.116,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "make"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "它不是 serious interview，也不是连续追问。更像把一个话题递出去：play, holiday, travel, school event, sports, shared activity。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 79,
      "start": 557.466,
      "end": 565.346,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "make"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "如果对方只给 very short answers，你就要判断：maybe this topic is not working, or maybe this person wants quiet."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 80,
      "start": 565.696,
      "end": 568.592,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "despair"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三个词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "despair"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 81,
      "start": 568.941,
      "end": 570.621,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "despair"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "despair"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 82,
      "start": 570.971,
      "end": 578.147,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "despair"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "despair"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是 the feeling that nothing is working and you are almost giving up，觉得没办法了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 83,
      "start": 578.497,
      "end": 583.469,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "despair"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "In despair, I asked her whether she was enjoying her dinner."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 84,
      "start": 583.819,
      "end": 593.755,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "despair"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里不是 life tragedy，而是 social despair。三个话题都只得到"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "No"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，主人公实在不知道还能问什么。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 85,
      "start": 594.105,
      "end": 601.1,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "despair"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "despair"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "帮我们听见他的尴尬，也帮最后一句 punchline 更响。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 86,
      "start": 601.45,
      "end": 611.47,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的 grammar 是 future continuous in polite questions，也就是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "will be doing"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "用来温和地问未来安排。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 87,
      "start": 611.82,
      "end": 618.172,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "直接一点的问法是："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Will you see it?"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这像是在问“你会不会去看？”"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 88,
      "start": 618.522,
      "end": 625.394,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "更柔和的寒暄是："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Will you be seeing it?"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "感觉像“这会不会在你的计划里？”"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 89,
      "start": 625.743,
      "end": 630.391,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "直接一点是："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Will you spend your holidays abroad?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 90,
      "start": 630.741,
      "end": 635.749,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "柔和一点是："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Will you be spending your holidays abroad this year?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 91,
      "start": 636.099,
      "end": 640.099,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "直接一点是："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Will you stay in England?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 92,
      "start": 640.449,
      "end": 644.449,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "柔和一点是："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Will you be staying in England?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 93,
      "start": 644.799,
      "end": 653.042,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这个"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "be doing"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "让问题不那么像逼对方立刻决定，而是像轻轻询问 a future arrangement。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 94,
      "start": 653.392,
      "end": 662.968,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "但语法再 polite，也不能保证对方想聊。Mrs. Rumbold 的三个"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "No"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "告诉主人公：topic not accepted。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 95,
      "start": 663.318,
      "end": 670.054,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后的 conditional 也先听意思："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "If you ate more and talked less, we would both enjoy our dinner."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 96,
      "start": 670.404,
      "end": 677.244,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这不是今天的重点语法课，而是 punchline：Please stop talking and let us eat."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 97,
      "start": 677.594,
      "end": 689.842,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以今天的板书可以记成：small talk question ="
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Will you be doing...?"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "；social signal = short answer；polite ending = know when to stop."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 98,
      "start": 690.191,
      "end": 698.471,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "现在把这课放进你的生活。想象你在 school dinner or camp meal，坐在一个不太熟的同学旁边。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 99,
      "start": 698.821,
      "end": 708.421,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "你的目标不是一直讲话，而是 open politely, try one or two light topics, and stop politely if the person gives very short answers。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 100,
      "start": 708.771,
      "end": 712.267,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可以这样开头："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Hi, I'm Li Ming."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
